data.description: This stunning home is located in Dover, DE, offering a convenient and desirable location. As you enter the home, you are greeted by a beautiful entrance that sets the tone for the rest of the house. The grand front door adds an elegant touch to the overall aesthetic. The home features four spacious bedrooms, all located on the same level for added convenience. This includes a master suite with an ensuite bathroom and two walk-in closets. The remaining bedrooms are well-sized and offer plenty of space for rest and relaxation. One of the standout features of this home is the inclusion of a laundry room on the same level as the bedrooms. This makes laundry day a breeze, eliminating the need to carry loads of laundry up and down the stairs. With 2 full bathrooms, there is plenty of convenience and comfort for everyone. The 2-car garage and 2-car driveway offer ample parking for you and your guests. Situated on a corner lot, this home offers privacy and a sense of space. The spacious finished basement provides additional living space, perfect for entertaining or creating a cozy retreat. Overall, this home offers a combination of elegance, functionality, and comfort. It is a perfect place to call home in Dover`s Lakeshore Village. The seller is offering a one year home warranty through APHW (a $499 value) for piece of mind. COME TO OUR OPEN HOUSE,  SATURDAY,  JAN 27TH FROM 12-3PM
